&lt;p>When I came to this planet, &lt;br>
I had a body full of memories but a mind without many memories. &lt;br>
And my mind was definitely without any biased memory. &lt;br>
I was full of life and everything was full of life for me. &lt;br>
Every happening was fresh, new, and full of excitement. &lt;br>
I bothered not anything more than food.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>